# EmailJS Setup Instructions
# 1. Sign up for free at: https://www.emailjs.com/
# 2. Go to "Email Services" -> "Add New Service" -> Select "Gmail" and connect your account. Copy the "Service ID".
# 3. Go to "Email Templates" -> "Create New Template". Configure the email template subject and content. Copy the "Template ID".
# 4. Go to "Account" -> "API Keys" -> Copy the "Public Key".
# 5. Replace the placeholder values below with your actual keys.

